quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  13,43,"Heefer…ďe …ďen hino wi'a: \"Wanaa a Nulaa…óo\". Maaku: \"Alla yonii seedee hakkunde am e mon, e …ďen jogitii…ďe ganndal Deftere nden"
  14,1,"Alif, Laam, Raa. (Ndee ko) Deftere nde Men jippini e maa…óa, fii yo yaltinir yim…ďe …ďen e ni…ďe faade e annoora, e duŇčayee Joomi ma…ď…ďe, haa e laawol Foolu…óo, Yettinii…óo"
  14,2,"Alla, On Mo woodani kala ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Bone woodani yeddu…ďe …ďen, immorde e lepte sattu…óe"
  14,3,"∆Āen …ďurdinoo…ďe nguurndam aduna …óam e dow laakara, …ďe faddoo e laawol Alla ngol, …ďe …óa…ď…ďana ngol oo√Īorgal. ∆Āen …óow wonii e majjere wo…ó…óunde"
  14,4,"Men nuliraali Nulaa…óo (woo), si wanaa e …óemngal yim…ďe makko …ďen, fii no o …ďannginirana …ďe. Alla no majjina on Mo muuyi, O fewna on Mo O muuyi. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  14,5,"Gom…óii Men nulirii Muusaa Aayeeje Amen …óen [wi'ugol Mo]: \"Yaltin yim…ďe maa …ďen e ni…ďe faade e annoora, anndintinaa …ďe √Īal…ói Alla …óin\". Pellet hino e …óum, tasakuyeeji kala munyoowo, yettoowo (neema)"
